Title: Sufficient conditions for the existence of Q-balls in gauge theories

Authors: Alexander Kusenko, Mikhail Shaposhnikov, and P. G. Tinyakov

Comments: 5 pages

Journal-ref: Pisma Zh.Eksp.Teor.Fiz. 67 (1998) 229; JETP Lett. 67 (1998) 247

